title: Live: Roar in front after pulsating start
text:
Wanderers v Roar: Follow the action as Western Sydney take on Brisbane at Pirtek Stadium in round 1 David Weiner FOX SPORTS Wanderers v Roar: Follow the action as Western Sydney take on Brisbane at Pirtek Stadium in round 1 David Weiner FOX SPORTS Frantic four goal half 1:07 
A-League: It was a crazy first half between Western Sydney and Brisbane with four goals to kick the A-League season off. October 8th 2015 4 minutes ago /video/video.news.com.au/Sport/Football/A-League/ 
THE A-League season kicks off tonight when Western Sydney Wanderers and Brisbane Roar clash at Pirtek Stadium. 
Both teams have a lot to prove in 2015-2016, as do their coaches, Tony Popovic and John Aloisi. 
Watch it all unfold with kick-off at 8pm EDT on Fox Sports 505, with a pre-game show from 7pm EDT. 
You can also follow the action, get video highlights and all the colour and excitement from season kick-off in our live blog below. Other Stories
